sequenceDiagram
  autonumber
  participant C as Client
  participant S as API Server
  Note over C,S: Initial fetch with ETag
  C->>S: GET /resource (no If-None-Match)
  S-->>C: 200 OK + ETag: "abc123" + Body
  Note over C: Cache ETag + body
  Note over C,S: Conditional GET
  C->>S: GET /resource (If-None-Match: "abc123")
  alt unchanged
    S-->>C: 304 Not Modified (no body)
  else changed
    S-->>C: 200 OK + ETag: "def456" + Body
  end
  Note over C,S: Backoff on overload
  C->>S: GET /resource (If-None-Match: "def456")
  S-->>C: 503 Service Unavailable + Retry-After: 5
  C-->>C: Exponential backoff, respect Retry-After